OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain this evening will turn more
OL,7,Fpersistent for a time in the early
OL,8,Fhours. South or southeasterly winds
OL,9,Fwill fresh and become occasionally
OL,10,Fstrong.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FEarly rain for Shetland, but
OL,13,Fmainly dry to start for Orkney. Then
OL,14,Fmainly dry and cloudy, rain returning
OL,15,Fto Orkney late afternoon and Shetland
OL,16,Fby evening.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,19,Famounts of cloud with a few showers on
OL,20,FFriday and Saturday. Risk of rain on
OL,21,FSunday.
